'''拿破崙酒店'''（{{lang-fr|Hotel Napoleon}}）是位於[[法國|法國]]首都巴黎8區[[凱旋門|凱旋門]]附近的一座[[酒店|酒店]]。2013年，拿破崙酒店被承認為五星級酒店，有許多名人，如海明威和馬里奧·巴爾加斯·略薩都曾經入住拿破崙酒店<ref>[http://www.parismatch.com/Culture-Match/Livres/Actu/Mario-Vargas-Llosa-le-Prix-Nobel-enfin-217874/ ''Mario Vargas Llosa, le Prix Nobel enfin''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.parismatch.com/Culture-Match/Livres/Actu/Mario-Vargas-Llosa-le-Prix-Nobel-enfin-217874/ |date=20120320123800 }}, ''[[Paris-Match|Paris-Match]]'' dated October 15, 2010, by Olivier O’Mahony: «I presented one of my stories to a literary contest organized by [[La_revue_française|La revue française]].  I won the first prize, which included a trip to [[Paris|Paris]]. What do you remember of that trip? I have wonderful memories! I stayed at the Hôtel Napoléon, where I remember meeting [[Miss_France|Miss France]] 1958, Annie Simplon. The manager, a Pole whose name was Mr. Makovski, took us to L’éléphant blanc, a fashinable nightclub, and I danced with her...»</ref>。
